reviewText: Unusual but highly entertaining buddy thriller, starring Ben Curtis (Steve, the Dell Dude) and Vincent Pastore (Big Pussy from the SOPRANOS).

Frank Vincent from my two favorites GoodFellas and Casino plays the mob boss Gaetano who is out to kill buisnessman Dante LeClair(Vincent Pastore) and Vinny Vella from Casino does the best as the ruthless Henry"Red" Dellarusso. Overall this was a low-budget film that was just all-right. If you like Vinny Vella or Frank Vincent I'd reccomend this one.
